title: Carers Encouraged to Take Free Flu Jab this Winter (Stockport Metropolitan Borough Council)
text: ( Source : Stockport Metropolitan Borough Council ) Stockport Council , alongside its partners, is encouraging carers - both paid and unpaid men and women - to take advantage of the free flu jab in order to reduce the risk to their own health
